<br>
In <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>pure melee</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->, the 62 water pet was averaging about 13-18 DPS higher per fight vs. crystalline golems(level 62 mobs).  Granted, it's procs landed and my pet's didn't, but I'm talking pure melee.  That's pretty impressive, in my opinion.  <br>
<br>
We are talking about a level 58 mage(me) vs. a level 65 mage.  So she had Burnout V and full haste caps compared to my Burnout IV and somewhat lower haste caps.  The mobs were also positioned for backstabbing, so that's another nod in the water pet's favor, and the epic was <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>still</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> relatively close in pure melee damage, despite being 11 levels lower.<br>
<br>
